high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the microwave oven on the other side of the room
Look up to the cupboard above the microwave, open the cupboard on the left, pick up the white mug, close the cupboard

Open the door of the microwave, place the mug on the left end of the plate in the microwave, close the door, turn the microwave on; once it turns off, open the microwave door, pick up the mug, close the door
Look up the cupboard above the microwave
Open the middle cupboard, place the mug in the center of the cupboard, close the cupboard
anns.task_desc: Get a mug from the cupboard, heat it in the microwave, put it back in the cupboard

high_descs: Turn to your left and go around the counter to your left, then head towards the cabinets above the microwave, at the left end of the kitchen counter.
Remove a coffee cup from the cabinet above the microwave.
Step down from the cabinets up top.
Place the coffee cup in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the coffee cup from the microwave.
Step back up to the cabinets above the microwave.
Put the coffee cup back in the right cabinet, above the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm coffee cup in the kitchen cabinet.

high_descs: Walk around the table and go to the microwave.
Grab the coffee cup from the top left cabinet above.
Locate the microwave under the cabinet.
Put the cup in the microwave and grab the cup afterwards.
Look at the top left cabinet again.
Put the cup in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Heat a mug and replace it.
